Each birthstone has a different meaning.

282
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:38,498
Amethyst are known
to bring a romantic relationship

283
00:16:38,581 --> 00:16:40,041
and represents love.

284
00:16:40,125 --> 00:16:41,793
Love...

285
00:16:43,878 --> 00:16:46,214
So pretty.

286
00:16:55,056 --> 00:16:57,225
May luck be ever in your favor.

287
00:17:10,071 --> 00:17:12,115
I get used to new things.

288
00:17:27,380 --> 00:17:28,757
An empty space...

289
00:17:29,340 --> 00:17:31,801
An absolutely empty space...

290
00:17:35,180 --> 00:17:37,015
