291
00:17:37,849 --> 00:17:39,267
Have you been waiting long?

292
00:17:39,350 --> 00:17:41,686
No, I got here early.

293
00:17:41,770 --> 00:17:45,148
We could have met near your place.
Next time I'll go there.

294
00:17:45,231 --> 00:17:46,149
Okay.

295
00:17:47,108 --> 00:17:51,112
