00:18:24,771 --> 00:18:28,525
Even if I just scribble,
I have amazing penmanship.

305
00:18:29,317 --> 00:18:33,363
If I recite, it becomes a poem.
When I hum, it becomes jazz.

306
00:18:33,446 --> 00:18:36,407
I do not operate on plans,
but by intuition.

307
00:18:37,200 --> 00:18:38,993
You believe in your intuition?

308
00:18:39,702 --> 00:18:42,372
In other words,
you're saying you're a genius.

309
00:18:42,455 --> 00:18:44,082
Am I?

310
00:18:44,165 --> 00:18:45,166
Are you not?

311
00:18:47,001 --> 00:18:48,044
Be patient.

312
00:18:48,127 --> 00:18:50,171
I'm organizing my thoughts.

313
00:18:51,172 --> 00:18:54,092
Now that I had some sweets,
it won't take long.

314
00:18:54,592 --> 00:18:55,969
I'll eat this.

315
00:18:57,887 --> 00:19:00,974
You said you can make yourself
look attractive to men, didn't you?

316
00:19:01,057 --> 00:19:04,561
You said you can, if you have a motive.
Was that a lie?

317
00:19:04,644 --> 00:19:06,062
No.

318
00:19:06,354 --> 00:19:08,773
Seduction is an easy task.

319
00:19:08,857 --> 00:19:11,317
This is about getting an ex back.

320
00:19:11,401 --> 00:19:13,862
It's not a simple matter.

321
00:19:14,904 --> 00:19:16,072
Seduction is easy?

322
00:19:16,155 --> 00:19:19,242
Why? You're still not convinced?

323
00:19:19,325 --> 00:19:22,495
Because nothing has been proven.
It's hard to be convinced.

324
00:19:22,829 --> 00:19:26,291
If you want proof,
