325
00:19:27,083 --> 00:19:29,711
Would that be even possible?

326
00:19:29,794 --> 00:19:30,837
Well...

327
00:19:32,255 --> 00:19:33,882
It goes like this.

328
00:19:34,257 --> 00:19:35,425
At first,

329
00:19:37,093 --> 00:19:40,221
I get a little closer to you...

330
00:19:46,728 --> 00:19:48,021
Look into your eyes...

331
00:19:52,066 --> 00:19:53,526
And smile.

332
00:19:58,823 --> 00:20:01,576
When you drink coffee, I do too.

333
00:20:08,333 --> 00:20:09,167
Whatever.

334
00:20:10,043 --> 00:20:12,045
When you rest your chin on your hand,

335
00:20:12,712 --> 00:20:14,088
I do that too.

336
00:20:18,426 --> 00:20:21,804
Coffee tastes good here.
It has good vibes too.

337
00:20:24,140 --> 00:20:27,393
