463
00:28:03,474 --> 00:28:06,185
What's that about?

464
00:28:06,268 --> 00:28:09,063
She thinks all men would fall for that?

465
00:28:10,648 --> 00:28:12,608
That's nuts.

466
00:28:14,235 --> 00:28:15,736
Jeez.

467
00:28:16,153 --> 00:28:18,197
I'm just going to sleep.

