00:28:47,768 --> 00:28:49,311
Good morning, Su-hyeok.

472
00:28:49,395 --> 00:28:50,938
Right, good morning.

473
00:28:52,857 --> 00:28:55,401
You just came to work, why the long face?

474
00:28:59,613 --> 00:29:02,616
-You've been in this mood these days.
-Have I?

475
00:29:03,993 --> 00:29:05,953
Is it because I'm not getting sleep?

476
00:29:06,036 --> 00:29:08,080
