00:32:49,009 --> 00:32:54,181
Sure. That's why we see
lots of those scenes on TV dramas.

534
00:32:54,264 --> 00:32:56,058
Because it's every woman's dream.

535
00:33:00,437 --> 00:33:01,480
If you say so.

536
00:33:03,273 --> 00:33:04,233
Okay!

537
00:33:06,568 --> 00:33:08,320
Our naive Jin-ho.

538
00:33:09,363 --> 00:33:11,615
This should end things
with the clubber, right?

539
00:33:11,699 --> 00:33:12,866
No doubt.

540
00:33:12,950 --> 00:33:16,412
Who wouldn't run away
from a surprise event in public?

541
00:33:18,706 --> 00:33:20,833
-Welcome.
-Hello.

542
00:33:20,916 --> 00:33:22,751
-Hello.
-Hello.

543
00:33:22,835 --> 00:33:23,752
Su-hyeok.

544
00:33:25,713 --> 00:33:26,964
Hello.

545
00:33:27,047 --> 00:33:28,674
-Hello.
