577
00:35:19,243 --> 00:35:21,829
"Can you see my happiness?"

578
00:35:24,665 --> 00:35:26,250
A glance that says all that.

579
00:35:29,127 --> 00:35:30,420
I don't think

580
00:35:32,172 --> 00:35:34,007
that was what the glance meant,

581
00:35:34,675 --> 00:35:36,885
