672
00:42:48,275 --> 00:42:50,610
That's not it...

673
00:42:55,532 --> 00:42:58,910
It's not that I like hearts.

674
00:42:59,661 --> 00:43:05,625
It's just that, Sang-jin, I like...

675
00:43:05,709 --> 00:43:07,419
That was too salty.

676
00:43:07,502 --> 00:43:08,545
It was.

677
00:43:08,628 --> 00:43:10,005
Are you having lunch?

678
00:43:10,088 --> 00:43:11,715
