679
00:43:13,049 --> 00:43:14,134
I just ate.

680
00:43:22,934 --> 00:43:24,144
Ms. Yeon?

681
00:43:27,230 --> 00:43:28,815
Yu-ri.

682
00:43:29,566 --> 00:43:31,443
What a coincidence seeing you here!

683
00:43:31,526 --> 00:43:33,069
