689
00:43:47,250 --> 00:43:48,960
I'm sorry.

690
00:43:49,711 --> 00:43:52,255
I was going to reach out to you.

691
00:43:52,714 --> 00:43:54,090
I'll visit sometime.

692
00:43:54,174 --> 00:43:56,968
Would you tell the crew I said hi?

693
00:43:57,052 --> 00:43:58,845
I will. Please do visit us.

694
00:43:58,928 --> 00:44:00,096
See you later.

695
00:44:00,180 --> 00:44:01,473
Take care.

696
00:44:04,642 --> 00:44:05,602
Mom.

697
00:44:06,186 --> 00:44:07,687
